title: Kim Davis freed, barred from interfering with licenses
text:
09 Kim Davis freed, barred from interfering with licenses 
CNN: Kim Davis is a free woman now, but what will she do when she returns to work?Could she end up behind bars again?The Kentucky clerk, who was held in contempt of court for refusing to issue same-sex marriage licenses, was released with a caveat she may not be willing to accept.
